PSXDataSelector.nativeStatement: SELECT * FROM PSX_ROLES WHERE NOT EXISTS (SELECT ROLEID FROM RXCOMMUNITYROLE WHERE RXCOMMUNITYROLE.ROLEID = PSX_ROLES.ID AND RXCOMMUNITYROLE.COMMUNITYID = :"PSXParam/communityid" ) ORDER BY PSX_ROLES.NAME ASC

SELECT * FROM WORKFLOWAPPS WHERE NOT EXISTS (SELECT WORKFLOWAPPID FROM RXWORKFLOWCOMMUNITY WHERE RXWORKFLOWCOMMUNITY.WORKFLOWAPPID = WORKFLOWAPPS.WORKFLOWAPPID AND RXWORKFLOWCOMMUNITY.COMMUNITYID = :"PSXParam/communityid" ) ORDER BY WORKFLOWAPPS.WORKFLOWAPPNAME ASC

SELECT * FROM CONTENTTYPES WHERE NOT EXISTS (SELECT CONTENTTYPEID FROM RXCONTENTTYPECOMMUNITY WHERE RXCONTENTTYPECOMMUNITY.CONTENTTYPEID = CONTENTTYPES.CONTENTTYPEID AND RXCONTENTTYPECOMMUNITY.COMMUNITYID = :"PSXParam/communityid" ) AND CONTENTTYPES.HIDEFROMMENU != 1 ORDER BY CONTENTTYPES.CONTENTTYPENAME ASC

SELECT a2.TEMPLATE_ID, a2.NAME, a3.CONTENTTYPEID, a3.CONTENTTYPENAME, a3.CONTENTTYPEDESC FROM PSX_TEMPLATE a2, CONTENTTYPES a3, PSX_CONTENTTYPE_TEMPLATE CTT WHERE (a2.TEMPLATE_ID IN (SELECT a.TEMPLATE_ID FROM PSX_TEMPLATE a WHERE NOT EXISTS (SELECT VARIANTID FROM RXVARIANTCOMMUNITY WHERE VARIANTID = a.TEMPLATE_ID AND COMMUNITYID = :"PSXParam/communityid"))) AND CTT.CONTENTTYPEID = a3.CONTENTTYPEID AND CTT.TEMPLATE_ID = a2.TEMPLATE_ID ORDER BY a3.CONTENTTYPENAME ASC, a2.NAME ASC

SELECT * FROM RXSYSCOMPONENT WHERE NOT EXISTS (SELECT COMPONENTID FROM RXCOMPONENTCOMMUNITY WHERE RXCOMPONENTCOMMUNITY.COMPONENTID = RXSYSCOMPONENT.COMPONENTID AND RXCOMPONENTCOMMUNITY.COMMUNITYID = :"PSXParam/communityid" ) ORDER BY RXSYSCOMPONENT.NAME ASC

SELECT * FROM RXSITES WHERE NOT EXISTS (SELECT SITEID FROM RXSITECOMMUNITY WHERE RXSITECOMMUNITY.SITEID = RXSITES.SITEID AND RXSITECOMMUNITY.COMMUNITYID = :"PSXParam/communityid" ) ORDER BY RXSITES.SITENAME ASC
